text: Rose of Cimarron is a 1952 American western movie. It was directed by Harry Keller. Actors include Mala Powers, Jack Beutel, Bill Williams, Dick Curtis, William Phipps, Irving Bacon, Monte Blue, and George Chandler. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1952 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Harry Keller
